description.en: Our aim is to give investors direct access to investment opportunities in the Crypto world and to enable entrepreneurs to raise capital for financing their projects in an efficient, cost effective, and secure way. CrowdWiz ecosystem is based on the concept of crowd wisdom, which utilizes the collective opinion of a group (the crowd) rather than that of an individual expert. We will use crypto financing (via Initial Coin Offering) for raising capital, as an integral part of our growth synergy with the contributors. The CrowdWiz ecosystem will be based on cryptographic token called WIZ, a tradeable token with the dual purpose of granting investors voting rights and exclusive access to the CrowdWiz ecosystem.
